  "detailed_description": "Demoniac TV is a roguelike where you exterminate various demons and fallen angels in waves. Equip yourself with weapons and upgrades and create the best strategy to survive this hell. In this battle, you will have to exorcise everything from the smallest demon to the seraphim.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Kill, kill, kill!</h2><br>You'll have to exorcize 12 types of demons. Good luck!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Build your strategy</h2><br>There are a lot of different upgrades. The arena will be chaotic!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Compete online</h2><br>Demoniac TV has a ranked mode, where you will have the opportunity to compete on a leaderboard with the best demon hunters in the world!",
  "about_the_game": "Demoniac TV is a roguelike where you exterminate various demons and fallen angels in waves. Equip yourself with weapons and upgrades and create the best strategy to survive this hell. In this battle, you will have to exorcise everything from the smallest demon to the seraphim.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Kill, kill, kill!</h2><br>You'll have to exorcize 12 types of demons. Good luck!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Build your strategy</h2><br>There are a lot of different upgrades. The arena will be chaotic!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Compete online</h2><br>Demoniac TV has a ranked mode, where you will have the opportunity to compete on a leaderboard with the best demon hunters in the world!",
